ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: yes, it's a great class and a great way to learn Coptic thoroughly

I would certainly recommend this course. I came out of the course feeling like I really had a solid grasp of the foundations of the language because the instructor had such high and consistent expectations.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This was a necessary language for my areas of interest.
I intend to do further study in Coptic literature for which this class is absolutely essential. I now feel capable and confident about continuing in my studies.
